Package org.apache.logging.log4j.core.pattern

Interface ArrayPatternConverter

All Superinterfaces:
PatternConverter
All Known Implementing Classes:
DatePatternConverter, FileDatePatternConverter, IntegerPatternConverter, LiteralPatternConverter
public interface ArrayPatternConverter extends PatternConverter
PatternConverters implement this interface to accept an array of objects when formatting.
